<body><div type="letter">
<pb facs="1078718" n="1"/>
<opener><salute>Viro Clarissimo, et toto Orbe Celeberrimo 
                    <lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Johanni Bernoulli</rs>
<lb/><abbr>S. P. D.</abbr>
<lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-102552517" type="person">Petrus Antonius Michelotti</rs></salute></opener>
<p>Qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> in <rs key="B_991170515019305501" type="letter">nuperrimis tuis Litteris</rs> exposuisti circa va<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>lorem Thaleri uncialis tandem communicavi Am<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>plissimo Moderatori <rs key="pers_DE-588-1089924410" type="person">Ruzzino</rs> Rure in Patriam
                <lb/>reverso; atque ab eodem audivi futurum fere impossi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>bile ut ipsi Triumviri Sapientissimi Patavini sci<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>licet <rs type="organisation">Archilycei</rs> <rs key="pers_DE-588-1089924410 pers_DE-588-1111043582 pers_DE-588-1178371670" type="persons">Moderatores</rs> salarium Ti<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>bi Vir Doctissime exhibeant atque persolvant
                <lb/>1500 Thalerorum uncialium quadringentis circiter
                <lb/>Louis d'or <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>quipollentium. Ipsi agnoscunt, atque
                <lb/>fatentur Te esse dignum etiam salario multo
                <lb/>maiore 1500 Thalerorum uncialium; sed quoniam
                <lb/>morem <rs type="organisation">Archilycei Patavini</rs> nequeunt mutare
                <lb/>atque transcendere in persolvendo salario
                <lb/>nemini unquam proposito, non sine moerore
                <lb/>coguntur <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> propositione dicti salarij abstinere,
                <lb/>Teque Mathematicorum Principem amittere. Possent
                <lb/>persolvere quidem salarium non solum 1500 Thale<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>rorum uncialium ver<choice><orig><g ref="#ugrav">ù</g></orig><reg>u</reg></choice>m etiam 2000, aut 3000
                <lb/>Thalerorum, et libenter hujusmodi salarium Tibi
                <pb facs="1078719" n="2"/>
<lb/>exhiberent atque solverent annuatim nisi antiqua
                <lb/>Magistratus consuetudo id vetaret, <choice><sic>e</sic><corr>et</corr></choice> si Excelsus <rs type="organisation">sena<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tus</rs> (cui subjectus <choice><orig><g ref="#est">[est]</g></orig><reg>est</reg></choice> Magistratus Moderatorum <rs type="organisation">Archi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>lycei Patavini</rs>) id permitteret. Salarium 1500 Tha<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>lerorum (quorum quilibet sesquifloreno germanico
                <lb/><choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>quipollet) Tibi Vir Doctissime proponunt, atque
                <lb/>annuatim persolvent, remque insuetam adhuc effi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ci<unclear>e</unclear>nt, ac Tuam Personam cuicumque Matheseos Profes<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>sori anteponent, quod sancte Tibi testor. Si huiusmo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>di recusas salarium res desperata est. Dolebo maxi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>me Vir incomparabilis de exitu infelici, quem labo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>res mei sortientur si Tu cum salario pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>dicto Pa<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tavium venire dedignaberis. Nemini proponetur
                <lb/>aut persolvetur huiusmodi salarium <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> Patavini
                <lb/>Archilycei Moderatoribus apud quos Tuum Nomen
                <lb/>in maxima est consideratione. Si venire renuis
                <lb/>Dominus Marchio <rs key="pers_DE-588-11887733X" type="person">Poleni</rs> Chatedram fortasse obti<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>nebit sed cum salario <choice><sic>solumodo</sic><corr>solummodo</corr></choice> 500 floreno<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<pb facs="1078720" n="3"/>
<lb break="no"/>rum germanorum; scilicet minus quam cum 3<choice><orig><g ref="#ndot">.</g></orig><reg></reg></choice><hi rend="sup">a</hi> par<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>te salari<choice><orig><g ref="#j">j</g></orig><reg>i</reg></choice> Tibi propositi ipse ad Mathematum
                <lb/><rs type="organisation">Cathedram</rs> promovebitur. Quisquis tandem fuerit
                <lb/>Professor, qui ad dictam <rs type="organisation">Cathedram</rs> promovebitur,
                <lb/>nunquam prima vocatione obtinebit plus quam
                <lb/>400, aut 500 florenos germanicos. Vides itaque Vir Ami<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>cissime quanti Te faciant isti <choice><abbr>Nobiliss.<hi rend="sup">i</hi></abbr><expan>Nobilissimi</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-1089924410 pers_DE-588-1111043582 pers_DE-588-1178371670" type="persons">Moderato<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>res</rs>.</p>
<p>Expectabo ultimam Tui determinatione quamprimum
                <lb/>super hac re.</p>
<p>Patavij alimenta parvo emuntur pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>tio; pluresque
                <lb/>sunt vacationum menses quibus sine expensis Domi
                <lb/>me<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> in hac inclita Civitate commorare posses. Pro<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>gressu temporis <choice><abbr>Clariss.<hi rend="sup">us</hi></abbr><expan>Clarissimus</expan></choice> Agnatus tuus <rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Nicolaus</rs> promo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>veretur Tui loco. Perpende qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>so h<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>c omnia, et si tibi
                <lb/>lubet suscipe Professorium munus in <rs type="organisation">Archilyc<choice><orig><g ref="#ehat">ê</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice>o Pata<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>vino</rs> cum salario annuo 1500 Thalerorum non uncia<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>lium, sed eorum, quorum quilibet sesquifloreno
                <lb/>germanico <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>quipollet.</p> <closer><salute>Interim vale, meque ad omnia
                <lb/>mandata Tua paratissimum crede.</salute>
<pb facs="1078721" n="4"/>
<lb/><dateline>Dabam <rs key="place_GEO-3164603" type="place">Venetiis</rs> <choice><abbr>a. d.</abbr><expan>ad diem</expan></choice> <date when="1714-11-21">21. Nov.<hi rend="sup">bris</hi> 1714</date></dateline></closer>
<postscript><p>P. S. <rs key="biblio_69NKSR46 biblio_W6BHQDM2 biblio_BS83R2A4 biblio_RTB4565Q" type="biblios">Fasciculus vestrorum librorum</rs> <rs key="place_GEO-3182164" type="place">Bergomum</rs> nondum pervenit.</p>
<p>Inposterum commercium epistolicum tecum ha<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>bere cuperem Vir <choice><abbr>Clariss.<hi rend="sup">e</hi></abbr><expan>Clarissime</expan></choice> in iis qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> respiciunt
                    <lb/>disciplinas mathematicas, ac medicas. Si mihi spem
                    <lb/>facies, atque mittendi ad Te litteras meas
                    <lb/>aliquando, facultatem concedes, nonnulla
                    <lb/>problemata physico-mechanico-medica maximi
                    <lb/>usus in Medicina Theoretica proponam; atque ex
                    <lb/>tuis solutionibus utilia semper, ac sublimia hau<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>riam.</p></postscript>
</div></body></text></TEI>